name: Liz Vicious
description:
Personal Hypernetwork made of Liz Vicious, an alt model active around 2005-2007. No real reason other than I always liked her look.

There was no shortage of material to train off of, but I limited to about 174 images.

The sample images were just simple prompts I used to give an example of what I'm going for.

I might retrain it later due to not really knowing how to make these that well.
